Package helio.materialiser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HelioMaterialiser
    This class is an implementation of the interface MaterialiserEngine
    HelioUtils
    This class provides a set of methods that ease the code writing
    MaterialiserOrchestrator
    This class manages a set of mappings, by ordering their elements according to their dependencies, and creating synchronous or asynchronous tasks to generate the RDF.
    OptimisedMapping
    This class is an alternative representation of a HelioMaterialiserMapping that generates the RDF more efficiently
